### NduthiRide — Riders endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@riderAccessToken = <paste_rider_access_token_here>

### ─── Get my rider profile ───────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/riders/me
Authorization: Bearer {{riderAccessToken}}

### ─── Update my rider profile ───────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/riders/me
Authorization: Bearer {{riderAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bikeModel": "Honda CG 125",
  "bikeRegistration": "KMBN 002B"
}

### ─── Toggle availability (online/offline) ──────────────────
### Note: Can also be done via WebSocket rider:toggle-availability event
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/riders/me/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{riderAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isAvailable": true
}

### ─── Get nearby available riders ───────────────────────────
### Used by the booking UI to show available riders on the map
GET {{baseUrl}}/riders/nearby?lat=-1.2921&lng=36.8219&radiusKm=5
Authorization: Bearer {{riderAccessToken}}

### ─── Get active ride for rider ─────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/riders/me/active-ride
Authorization: Bearer {{riderAccessToken}}
